{"tid":409022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱睇完屎個post，我有個疑問","createTime":"2017-09-21T16:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T17:37:15.000Z","uid":32298,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a067e39b4bc7798216d858c8ddbe0466d77837c","tid":409022,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱睇完個屎post，我就cap咗張圖上group同我啲朋友討論啦，咁個group入面有男有女，其中有兩個女仔就話好核突咁啦，之後講講下就講到平時點抆屎<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   女仔：fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：你點解會覺得張圖核突架，平時爆石都會見到啲屎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女仔fd：我平時望唔到架喎，好多年都無望過！<br />\n<br />\n我：咁抆屎果陣望唔到？<br />\n<br />\n女仔fd：點會望到啊，坐喺度抆架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：下...點會坐喺度架，點抆到啊<br />\n<br />\n女仔fd：下，你平時企喺度抆架？哈哈哈...<br />\n<br />\n我：坐係度抆唔會hi到手？邊度有位俾你伸隻手入去抆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就想問下各位巴絲平時係點樣抆屎，尤其係